Gazit-Globe Raised to ‘Buy’ From ‘Market Perform’ at Leader

-- B y   S u s a n   L e r n e r
-- 
2011-09-18T11:59:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-18/gazit-globe-raised-to-buy-from-market-perform-at-leader.html
Gazit-Globe Ltd. (GLOB)  was raised to
“buy” from “market perform” and its share-price estimate
increased to 45 shekels from 40 shekels at  Leader Capital
Markets (LDRC)  Ltd., according to a research report e-mailed today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
